description.en: Hiya! My name is Erisly, your friendly neighbourhood goddess! I use my powers and talents to play as a "Discord Bot", where I provide you some quality features and commands for your Discord Server!
description.ga_IE: Hiya!Is é an t-ainm atá orm, tá an bandia comharsanachta cairdiúil!Úsáidim mo chumhachtaí agus mo bhuanna a imirt mar "bot discord", áit a gcuirim roinnt gnéithe agus orduithe ar fáil duit do do fhreastalaí discord!
